steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jit015m" and Comment "[INDEX-ALL]"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit015m" display
When I add new column with Name "indexstring" Type "string" for Table name "jit015m"
When I open popup to see column infos Name "indexstring" of table with Name "jit015m"
When I check checkbox popup Name "Indexed"
When I press Save button modal popup
